<section class="help-card">
  <div class="help-card__eyebrow">Planning</div>
  <h2 class="help-card__title">A practical leasing timeline</h2>

  <div class="timeline-card">
    <div class="timeline-card__step">
      <strong>1. Define requirements</strong>
      <p>Clarify size, use, budget, and location before starting your search.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="timeline-card__step">
      <strong>2. Tour and compare</strong>
      <p>Visit a focused set of options and compare tradeoffs—not just price.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="timeline-card__step">
      <strong>3. Negotiate terms</strong>
      <p>Review lease structure, rent increases, improvements, and responsibilities.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="timeline-card__step">
      <strong>4. Prepare for occupancy</strong>
      <p>Allow time for setup, utilities, compliance, and any buildout before moving in.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>